{"tid":2070492,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電訊：公司5G網絡並不限於使用華為設備，能兼用不同供應商","createTime":"2020-06-19T07:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T12:21:02.000Z","uid":109923,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf159ecefef8bf941f4e61cfb409eeff5af66cb","tid":2070492,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"自上月美國商務部宣佈，無論哪個地方幫華為或其關聯公司生產晶片，只要使用被列入管制清單的半導體製造設備、軟件或技術，需事先向美方申請，並予120日緩衝期，華為從此踏入「盲搶晶片潮」。彭博更以「緊急狀態」來形容，料其晶片庫存將在2021年初用完。<br />\n<br />\n事件或波及香港電訊業。據了解，除數碼通（315）表明採用愛立信設備外，中移動香港、香港電訊（6823）及和記電訊（215）都有使用華為5G設備。香港電訊指，公司5G網絡並不限於使用華為設備，能兼用不同供應商，即使華為受晶片限購亦不會有影響，公司會繼續伸延網絡覆蓋至全港各區；<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其餘兩間則未予回應。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n全文請click link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200619/64DCQI3U4MNKCJMGWRUH65SHM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200619%2F64DCQI3U4MNKCJMGWRUH65SHM4%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=c8dd5d9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200619%2F64DCQI3U4MNKCJMGWRUH65SHM4%2F&h=6ca07a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200619/64DCQI3U4MNKCJMGWRUH65SHM4/</a>"},{"pid":"697ad1a34479089578e5cea59dbfd44de9fe1ada","tid":2070492,"uid":1886,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"數碼通已夠人，用 3"},{"pid":"9d27d8cec7278b029327bf57ad1f3723ac913339","tid":2070492,"uid":1089,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"csl同網上爬肯轉既話我下次同佢續約續隻最貴既plan又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要求唔高，比返以前隻NEC modem我就夠"},{"pid":"236e29f1b4b848d31917c00dc1b70be606175274","tid":2070492,"uid":1886,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9d27d8cec7278b029327bf57ad1f3723ac913339","tid":2070492,"uid":1089,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4